<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="ie=edge">
    <title>Document</title>
</head>
<style>

*{
  font-weight: 100;
  letter-spacing: 2px;
  color: #555;
  font-family: 微軟正黑體;
}
body{
    background-color: #d1d1d1;
    padding: 0px;
    margin: 0px;
    box-sizing: border-box;
    border-top: solid 20px #f24;
    border-bottom: solid 20px #f24;
}
body,html{
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
}
h3{
    margin-top: 40px;
    color: #333;
    text-align: center;
    position: fixed;
    bottom: 10px;
    width: 100%;
}
.name{
    font-weight: 800;
    font-size: 28px;
}
.job{
    margin-top: 0px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
}
.little_eng{
    margin-left: 10px;
    font-size: 11px;
}  
.namecard{
  background-color: #eee;
  width: 350px;
  height: 200px;
  margin-left: auto;
  margin-right: auto;
  cursor: pointer;
  box-shadow: 10px 5px 50px rgba(255,255,255,0.4),5px 5px 30px rgba(50,50,50,0.2);
  border: solid 1px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
  padding: 22px;
  margin-top: 120px;
  border-radius: 8px;
  transition-duration: 0.5s;
  overflow: hidden;
  position: relative;
  transform-origin: 50% 50%;
}
.namecard:hover{
    transform: translateY(-5px) translateX(-5px);
    box-shadow: 10px 10px 30px rgba(50,50,50,0.3);
}     
.namecard h5{
    color:  #f24;
}
.namecard P{
    font-size: 10px;
    line-height: 20px;
}    
.namecardtext{
    position: absolute;
    left: -5px;
    bottom: 100px;
    color: rgba(0,0,0,0.03);
    font-size: 300px;
} 
hr{
    text-decoration: none;
    display: block;
    border-style: none;
    border-top-style: solid;
} 
.circle{
    width: 70px;
    height: 70px;
    position: absolute; 
    right: -30px;
    top:-30px;
    background-color:#5599FF;
    border-radius: 100%;
    transition-duration: 1s;
}  
  
.circle2{
    width: 100px;
    height: 100px;
    left: initial;
    right: -35px;
    top: -35px;
    background-color: initial;
    border: solid 3px #5599FF;
    transition-delay: 0.4s;
}
.namecard:hover .circle1{
    transform-origin: 50% 50%;
    transform: scale(1.2);
}
.namecard:hover .circle2{
    transform-origin: 50% 50%;
    transform: scale(1.3);
} 
</style>
<body>
    <div class="namecardtext">NAMECARD</div>
        <div class="namecard">
            <div class="circle circle1"></div>
            <div class="circle circle2"></div>
            <h2 class="name">王冠勛
            <span class="little_eng">(Gary Wang)</span>
            </h2>
            <h5 class="job">軟體工程師</h5>
            <hr/>
            <p class="description">使用過的工具:HTML、CSS、JavaScript、Python、Firebase、C#、Node.js、Express.js、jQuery、Bootstrap、MS SQL、Git、Herku、React.js。</p>
        </div>
                          
</body>
</html>